<text id="02-output-contract" title="Cross-Channel CPA Rollup Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for one rollup row. Validator enforces gross-spend presence, dedup-ID coverage, and view-through separation.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/cross-channel-cpa-rollup.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "week", "channel", "gross_spend_usd", "attributed_conversions",
    "self_reported_conversions", "view_through_count", "cpa_gross",
    "incremental_over_organic", "cpa_incremental",
    "cohort_d30_retention", "attribution_policy_version"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "week": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d{4}-W\\d{2}$"},
    "channel": {"type": "string", "minLength": 3},
    "gross_spend_usd": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
    "attributed_conversions": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
    "self_reported_conversions": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
    "view_through_count": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
    "cpa_gross": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
    "incremental_over_organic": {"type": "integer"},
    "cpa_incremental": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
    "cohort_d30_retention": {"type": ["number", "null"], "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
    "cohort_d60_retention": {"type": ["number", "null"], "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
    "cohort_d90_retention": {"type": ["number", "null"], "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
    "attribution_policy_version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"},
    "notes": {"type": "string"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "week": "2026-W20",
  "channel": "Meta-paid",
  "gross_spend_usd": 4800.0,
  "attributed_conversions": 32,
  "self_reported_conversions": 51,
  "view_through_count": 18,
  "cpa_gross": 150.0,
  "incremental_over_organic": 22,
  "cpa_incremental": 218.18,
  "cohort_d30_retention": 0.71,
  "cohort_d60_retention": null,
  "cohort_d90_retention": null,
  "attribution_policy_version": "1.2.0",
  "notes": "Includes $600 agency fee."
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "week": "W20",
  "channel": "Meta",
  "gross_spend_usd": 4800,
  "attributed_conversions": 51,
  "view_through_count": 18,
  "cpa_gross": 94
}
]]></code>
    <note>week pattern wrong; missing self_reported / incremental_over_organic / cpa_incremental / cohort_d30 / attribution_policy_version; attributed includes view-through (CPA suspiciously low).</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Required cadence">
    <list>
      <item>Weekly rebuild + publish (script + dashboard refresh).</item>
      <item>Attribution-policy file reviewed quarterly; changes are versioned.</item>
      <item>Cohort retention requires ≥ 30 days of post-acquisition data — recent weeks show partial cohort with explicit "in progress" flag (null).</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden">
    <list>
      <item>CPA computed against self_reported_conversions instead of attributed_conversions (violates rule single-attribution-model).</item>
      <item>gross_spend_usd excludes agency / production fees (violates rule gross-spend).</item>
      <item>view_through added to attributed_conversions without an incrementality study (violates rule single-attribution-model).</item>
      <item>Organic baseline absent → incremental_over_organic == attributed (violates rule organic-baseline).</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-cross-channel-cpa-rollup.py">Validator script</reference>
  <reference path="templates/rollup-sheet.csv">Sheet header template</reference>
</text>
